    "C Pairwise F ST estimates for each population replicates per genotype, population, and resistance/susceptibility class varied (Additional file 2: Fig.",
    "Transcriptome experimental design and treatmentTo randomize environmental variation in the greenhouse (conditions described above), plants were distributed across 6 trays (~30 plants / tray) and trays were distributed across 2 adjacent benches (< 60 cm apart) (Additional file 2: Fig.",
